<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM13.6">
<l>naṭaiyoṉ ṟillā vulakattu nanta kōpaṉ makaṉeṉṉum</l>
<l>koṭiya kaṭiya tirumālāl kuḷappuk kūṟu koḷappaṭṭup</l>
<l>puṭaiyum peyara killēṉāṉ pōṭkaṉ mititta vaṭippāṭṭil</l>
<l>poṭittāṉ koṇarntu pūcīrkaḷ pōkā vuyireṉ ṉuṭampaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I am even unable to move, having been caused great misery by the cruel, harsh Tirumāl</l>
<l>Called Nandagopa’s son, in this world devoid of [proper] behaviour!</l>
<l>Bring the dust from the footprints made by the deceitful person</l>
<l>And smear [it] upon my body from which the life-breath does not leave!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
